sjp69d45.en:
The formula for calculating the revenue-sharing amount - internal deduction
Headquarters: (Transaction amount - Handling fee) * Headquarters' share of the account;
Store: Order amount - Handling fee - headquarters' share amount.
External buckle
Headquarters: Transaction amount * Headquarters' share of the revenue;
Store: Order amount - Headquarters revenue-sharing amount.

57ht306u.en:
Formula for calculating the share amount
Internal buckle
Headquarters: (Transaction amount - Handling fee) * Headquarters' share of the account;
Dealer: (Transaction amount - handling fee) * Dealer's share of the revenue;
Store: Order amount - Handling fee - headquarters' share amount - Dealer's share amount.
External buckle
Headquarters: Transaction amount * Headquarters' share of the revenue;
Dealer: Transaction amount * Dealer's share of revenue;
Store: Order amount - headquarters revenue-sharing amount - Dealer revenue-sharing amount.

